description="The upgrade preserves the current Web Studio port, Redis database number, administrator credentials, and Provider configuration."
adminDescription="The upgrade only refreshes the application and offline dependencies. It does not reset the administrator account, password, or Gateway API Key. Administrator credential recovery remains available in package settings after the upgrade."

